         fhir:Extension.valueString [ fhir:value "/*\n@input: The latest tetanus and diphtheria dose was administered less than 4 weeks ago\n@pseudocode: Today's date − latest \"Date and time of vaccination\" (where \"Vaccine type\" = \"Tetanus and diphtheria-containing vaccines\") < 4 weeks\n@code: The latest tetanus and diphtheria dose was administered less than 4 weeks ago-132\n@decision: IMMZ.D2.DT.DTP.Pregnancy starting with 3 doses: Diphtheria and tetanus vaccination schedule in pregnant women who received 3 childhood DTP doses\n*/\ndefine \"The latest tetanus and diphtheria dose was administered less than 4 weeks ago\":\n  \"Date of Latest Td Dose\" is not null\n    and duration in weeks between \"Date of Latest Td Dose\" and Today < 4" ]
       ], [
